Description of problem:
All the geo rep config options are resetted when user tries to reset one option.

Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
rhsc-3.1.0-0.60.el6.noarch

How reproducible:
Always

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Create a geo rep session.
2. Click master volume subtab-> Geo Replication-> Options.
3. Change few config options and click ok.
4. Open Options window and reset only one option.
4. Verify the option which is been resetted gets updated in CLI.

Actual results:
All the config options are reset back to default value in CLI.

Expected results:
Only the option which is been resetted should be updated in CLI.

Additional info:
Removing blocker flag as this bug was not reproducible
Please reopen if you hit this issue again
